\f0\b\fs38 \cf0 How do I delete a flight or trip?\
\pard\pardeftab720\qj\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 \
Simply tap on the \'93Edit\'94 button after you expanded the trip in which you want to delete something. You have the option to delete the whole trip or a single flight. Alternatively you can also swipe the flight you want to delete, just like you would do with an email. If the flight you deleted is the last one in the trip, the trip will automatically be deleted as well.\
