\f1\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qj\partightenfactor0

\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \'a0
\fs32 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qj\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf2 The app will always update with your TripIt account whenever it is opened, including coming from background. If you are impatient or this does not seem to work you can always tap the button in the settings screen to refresh the data. However if you modified the trip on TripIt, after adding it to FlightStatus, you will have to delete it from FlightStatus first before the new data is fetched. This is to prevent duplicate trips from showing up. \
